<div class="p">Upheld a little mote,</div>
<div class="p">Which in that holy sky did float,</div>
<div class="p">And, splendid to behold,</div>
<div class="p">Had a wee halo with gilt coat,</div>
<div class="p">And whereon many dote.</div>
