<div class="p">With limning light behind, it bloomed,</div>
<div class="p">A mazing bibelot,</div>
<div class="p">That charmed all vision from the show</div>
<div class="p">Of trinkets, and assumed</div>
<div class="p">Preeminence amid the glow</div>
<div class="p">Of its <em>milieu</em> like cameo.</div>
