<div class="p">So though I know you not, fair point,</div>
<div class="p">You bloom in no less light,</div>
<div class="p">Hair streaming, silken, white;</div>
<div class="p">The skies above anoint</div>
<div class="p">Your aspect like a kite</div>
<div class="p">In stark, illumined flight.</div>
<p>Â </p>
<div class="p">You float uncertain of your self</div>
<div class="p">Upon the field of thought,</div>
<div class="p">In reddish-amber fancy caught,</div>
<div class="p">As mystically as an elf,</div>
<div class="p">And hidden as an elf; and sought</div>
<div class="p">By many and, in fine, for naught.</div>
